  "commit_message": "Clarify Sentinel channel label: Microsoft Sentinel (Azure Log Analytics) (#138)\n\n* fix(ui): clarify Sentinel channel label as Microsoft Sentinel (Azure Log Analytics)\n\nThe SENTINEL channel ships events to an Azure Log Analytics workspace;\nSentinel is the usual consumer but any Log Analytics workspace works.\nKeep the enum value (no migration) and clarify the user-facing labels:\ndropdown option becomes \"Microsoft Sentinel (Azure Log Analytics)\",\ntype chip becomes \"Microsoft Sentinel\".\n\nCo-Authored",
